{"tid":1258232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荃灣港安 u burn with us!!!!!!","createTime":"2019-06-26T04:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T04:04:14.000Z","uid":267007,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5e10d5a4c169770103185fb98e23675825317ba8","tid":1258232,"uid":267007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T04:04:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190626/20713286\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190626%2F20713286&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmYuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=3c7a8658\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190626%2F20713286&h=773f2865\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190626/20713286</a><br />\n6.12金鐘警方暴力鎮壓示威，荃灣港安醫院向警方通報一名在衝突中受傷的示威者下落，最終該示威者在荃灣仁濟醫院被捕。工黨社區幹事趙恩來、荃灣區議員李洪波等人昨到港安抗議，要求院方管理層道歉，以及承諾不向第三者提供病者私隱。<br />\n<br />\n工黨一行六人向港安醫院遞交請願信，港安派人接收信件。趙恩來說，如港安醫院未有回應訴求，未來會採取一系列行動，包括一人一信向國際評核認證機構投訴港安出賣病人私隱、發動居民抵制港安等，強調有關行動原則是不會影響醫院運作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 篤灰篤到你咁開心呀拿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}